params._initialOwners: The list of privileged shareholder's names
params._shareholderAddress: The list of privileged shareholder's addresses.
params._shares: The list of shares assigned to each privileged shareholder.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

proxiableUUID().details: Implementation of the ERC-1822 {proxiableUUID} function. This returns the storage slot used by the implementation. It is used to validate the implementation's compatibility when performing an upgrade. IMPORTANT: A proxy pointing at a proxiable contract should not be considered proxiable itself, because this risks bricking a proxy that upgrades to it, by delegating to itself until out of gas. Thus it is critical that this function revert if invoked through a proxy. This is guaranteed by the `notDelegated` modifier.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

params._alreadyMinted: The number of Bananashares Tokens that an `AssetFactoryProxy` has already requested to mint for its users.
params._numberOfAssetShares: The number of shares in an `AssetFactoryProxy` sold by a privileged shareholder.
params._tokenReceiver_1: The address of the token receiver (regular)
params._tokenReceiver_2: The address of the token receiver (privileged)

params._commission_for_privileged: The commission for the privileged shareholders.
params._min_sell_offer: The minimal price per share in a new offer.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

upgradeToAndCall(address,bytes).details: Upgrade the implementation of the proxy to `newImplementation`, and subsequently execute the function call encoded in `data`. Calls {_authorizeUpgrade}. Emits an {Upgraded} event.

params._addr: The address to send the Ether.

getAssetInstanceByHash(bytes32).notice: Returns the address of AssetInstance contract for specific hash.

getAssetInstanceHashByAddress(address).notice: Returns the hash of AssetInstance contract for specific address.

getAssetInstanceImplementation().notice: Returns the implementation address of AssetInstances.

sendTokenMintingOrder(address,address,ui.notice: Sends the token minting order to the BananasharesToken contract.

withdraw().notice: Withdraws Ether collectd by the protocol.

withdrawTo(address,uint256).notice: Sends a specific amount of Ether from the protocol's balance to a defined address.
